{"tid":1671288,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"設阱自踩奸有奸輸 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-10-23T11:28:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T12:36:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c2e15242ae1c13d6759b76bbedd73db4ad3da0dd","tid":1671288,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:28:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191023/20791757/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191023%2F20791757%2F&d=krzUv%2FzG327U7XiGlMZ3yMyzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=8da4d24e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191023%2F20791757%2F&h=996d8b76\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191023/20791757/</a><br />\n<br />\n設阱自踩奸有奸輸 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191023/large/1571728725_09e9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191023%2Flarge%2F1571728725_09e9.jpg&h=6ae9e57d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭縱容下的黑警，水炮車衝擊清真寺，是恃勢橫行之報復行動。<br />\n<br />\n之前民陣岑子杰遭不明來歷的蒙面南亞人襲擊，頭破血流倒在街頭，已是「一條龍」陰謀部署，買兇借刀殺人，企圖惹起族群仇恨，示威者被「鬼」帶風向，在1020遊行時反擊重慶大廈和清真寺──誰料族群大和解也大團結，本地穆斯林組織出聲明譴責暴力，南亞團體也有廿多人攜果籃探望。岑寬心包容，示威群眾中多有有識之士，分別在清真寺門外舉牌呼籲：禮待宗教，守護寺院。人情世故江湖歷練，是陰毒妹仔和低能黑警所不懂的。出事了！<br />\n<br />\n水炮車射出帶胡椒之顏色毒水兩次，大面積染藍，都是停定瞄準寺外的議員記者市民發射，肆無忌憚褻瀆寺院，挑戰伊斯蘭教──示威者不中計，設局者自踩陷阱，國際震怒，一個字：「蠢」！<br />\n<br />\n林鄭嚇得與黑警高層上門求諒，領便衣「清潔」（又跟市民口水尾），hea做5分鐘收工，見他們不情不願，笑死。但一向撐警的印度協會前主席，因警方完全過界，不接受道歉。<br />\n<br />\n黑警得罪上帝耶穌黃大仙車公關公，但得罪不起真主阿拉，藍液瘋狂發射，不怕後果嗎？別以為到過新疆受訓就把香港當新疆。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"7ee25ab79d6dcba6338d9953034f422b3777a661","tid":1671288,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf554797e51b4e51881f5c59dc1eb1cb164d9ff0","tid":1671288,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e701d81493498556bd9202c2abf2bdcd93828933","tid":1671288,"uid":294635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-23T12:36:24.000Z","msg":"李碧華成日講野都咁到位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}